            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9D%A1%E9%86%92%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%98%E5%BE%88%E7%B4%AF%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9D%A1%E9%86%92%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%98%E5%BE%88%E7%B4%AF%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#睡醒了还很累是一种病#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[困]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[困]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%A0%E7%9D%A1%E5%BE%97%E9%A6%99%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%A0%E7%9D%A1%E5%BE%97%E9%A6%99%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#你睡得香吗#</span></a>专家介绍：慢性疲劳综合征除了疲劳以外，最主要的特征之一就是休息后疲劳难以恢复。除此之外，有些人还会出现肌肉疼痛、关节不舒服、睡眠不好等症状。慢性疲劳综合征多发于哪些人群呢？是什么原因导致的呢？👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4886041660948582" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hcl7c336c9j21hc0u0wi5.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/iutQD70Jlx084lBs6e0U01041201um1j0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680585546&amp;ssig=BTi7sLrWAQ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/6dfDxxMclx084lBqUJm801041200KpuP0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680585546&amp;ssig=P00cJO1S%2FT&a