            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91%E8%B5%B07000%E6%AD%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91%E8%B5%B07000%E6%AD%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#建议每天最少走7000步#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>近日，“2023版运动处方中国专家共识”发布，合理运动要遵循6个原则：运动频率、强度、方式、时间、总量、运动进阶。<br><br>世界卫生组织推荐：成年人<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8150%E8%87%B3300%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89%E5%BC%BA%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%A7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8150%E8%87%B3300%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89%E5%BC%BA%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%A7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#建议每周150至300分钟中等强度有氧#</span></a>运动，或75～150分钟较大强度的有氧运动。（人民日报）<br><br>所以，你今天的运动量达标了吗？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcmlcymedsj20en0fzq3s.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
